#. metadata.json->description
msgid ""
"Click on the applet to make a screenshot of the selected region and "
"immediately upload it. The resulting link will be copied to your clipboard. "
"The file will also be saved in your ~/Pictures directory. Makes use of the "
"packages 'xdg-user-dir', 'gnome-screenshot' and 'xclip'."
msgstr ""
